race.comment: TAKE AIM (6) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten half a length (23.61) behind Paw London at this track. Top chance in this line up. PAGODA GROWLER (1) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when second (27.94) in a Mix 6/7 over 485m at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. PAW VELDRON (2) comes off an average effort last start when eighth at Warrnambool over 390m behind FRED THE FOX (23.47) in a Mix 6/7. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from eight starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. SPRING QUIZ (7) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.
